{%- block cp_config_audit -%}
{%- if 'cp_audit' in ansible_run_tags or 'cp_config_audit' in ansible_run_tags or 'all' in ansible_run_tags -%}
{%- raw %}
# 3 Control Plane Configuration

## 3.1 Authentication and Authorization

### 3.1.1 Client certificate authentication should not be used for users (Manual)

**Audit:**  

**Remediation:** Alternative mechanisms provided by Kubernetes such as the use of OIDC should be implemented in place of client certificates.

**Result:**

{%- endraw -%}

{%- if kube_config_data.users is defined -%}
{%- set ns = namespace(counter=0) -%}
{% for user in kube_config_data.users %}
{%- if user.user is defined %}
{%- if user.user|dict2items|selectattr('key', 'match', '^client-certificate')|list|length > 0 %}
{%- set ns.counter = ns.counter + 1 %}
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
{%- endfor %}
{%- if ns.counter == 0 %}
 PASS  
{% else %}
 FAIL  
{% endif %}
{%- raw -%}
**List of users using Client Certificate Authentication:**  
{% endraw %}
{% for user in kube_config_data.users %}
{{ '- `' + user.name|string + '`\n' if user.user is defined and user.user|dict2items|selectattr('key', 'match', '^client-certificate')|list|length > 0 }}
{%- endfor %}
{% raw %}
Desired Setting: **None**
{% endraw %}
{%- else %}
 FAIL  
{% endif %}
{% raw %}
